{"tid":1516174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係Starbucks買左杯咖啡 決定唔會再幫襯","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:27:34.000Z","uid":278944,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3a19653e87a29ee293972fedb14d5a821b5f6e50","tid":1516174,"uid":278944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"話說琴日係statbucks買左杯skim milk latte 加左d肉桂 拎到番公司飲既時候覺得鹹鹹地 <br />\n我諗左勁耐 會唔會係d肉桂問題 拎左番去Starbucks <br />\nD staff輪流試吓啲肉桂 話可能有d問題 換過杯俾我<br />\n我番番上公司 再飲既時候 又覺得鹹鹹地<br />\n我已經打算放棄杯野<br />\n但收工嘅時候都係去多次同佢哋講杯野好鹹<br />\n話可能係啲咖啡豆鹹 再拎過杯俾我<br />\n<br />\n到最後我依然覺得杯野係鹹 冇飲到<br />\n擺咗喺我個杯(Starbucks嘅保溫杯)入邊擺咗一晚 就變到而家咁啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 張相係洗杯嘅時候到左佢出嚟影嘅 唔會再買<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cnFddv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cnFddv.png&h=4fb7d0db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a605578272618a9727a2e618a8920af5ac4c0c0d","tid":1516174,"uid":105911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，乜撚野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b614f5f185490dc0081cd1358de3ce00171f49b","tid":1516174,"uid":278944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a605578272618a9727a2e618a8920af5ac4c0c0d","tid":1516174,"uid":105911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，乜撚野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"格左一晚既skim milk latte<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faed07e4a83f00f1ba5341822730c99f321795a","tid":1516174,"uid":241186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a19653e87a29ee293972fedb14d5a821b5f6e50","tid":1516174,"uid":278944